51, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 306, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.7159722665780444, \"rank\": 0.3910182695318564, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recommended  This is a third successive Olympic final for O'Donovan, who won silver alongside brother Gary in Rio before going one better alongside McCarthy three years ago.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999533884, \"rank\": 4.660058887248424e-10, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.7159722665780444, \"rank\": 0.3910182695318564, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During their time as a pair, O'Donovan and McCarthy have won three world gold medals and two European gold medals to go with their gold from Tokyo.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.7159722665780444, \"rank\": 0.3910182695318564, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9