 after their progression from the heats, and he once again raised issue with it on Wednesday morning with a cheeky remark about their \\\"David and Goliath\\\" standing.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999907670916083, \"rank\": 3.78780575593243e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul O'Donovan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.688992379768573e-14, \"text\": \"Goliath\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"https://www.balls.ie/olympics/paul-odonovan-ireland-olympics-prediction-606264  READ HERE:Global Olympics Audience Amazed By Astonishing Lift And Catch By Ireland Sevens Team  READ HERE:Emotions Get Better Of Proud Daniel Wiffen During Irish Anthem After Magical Gold  After the Irish duo of Paul O'Donovan and Fintan McCarthy took a routine victory in the heats of the lightweight double sculls earlier this week, O'Donovan joked that their low seeding meant they were \\\"the little Davids of this world going up against the Goliaths.\\\"\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazed\", \"score\": 0.9999999815281628, \"rank\": 1.847190061774093e-08, \"text\": \"Amazed\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://