the top-seeded Swiss pair.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paul O'Donovan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_O'Donovan\"}, {\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintan McCarthy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.7159722665780444, \"rank\": 0.3910182695318564, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 2126, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Gillick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Gillick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Gillick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Gillick\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9990827280970367, \"rank\": 0.0009176543064392951, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gillick asked O'Donovan whether Ireland had filled the role of David or Goliath in Wednesday's race, and the answer was exactly what you might have expected.\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999907670916083, \"rank\": 3.78780575593243e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.688992379768573e-14, \"text\": \"Goliath\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goliath\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, the little Davids again.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a big, big upset, so it was.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swiss are number two ranked, way above us, fastest time in the heat.\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2469, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9990827280970367, \"rank\": 0.0009176543064392951, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are happy to be able to put out that performance.\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All year we have been throwing the kitchen sink at them and just could not get ahead of them.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have had an answer to us every single time we have raced this year but not today.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are hoping Friday we will be able to produce the goods again.\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the jabs, you do get the sense that O'Donovan and McCarthy are delighted to be back to their best after some struggles earlier this year.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2898, \"end\": 2906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.7159722665780444, \"rank\": 0.3910182695318564, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McCarthy would share an intriguing stat with Gillick which suggests that the Irish duo are becoming sharper and sharper as the competition goes on.\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2987, \"end\": 2995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.7159722665780444, \"rank\": 0.3910182695318564, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 3064, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.965362981629615, \"rank\": 0.03498788419798767, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was solid, we are trying to build on our heat.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it was solid enough.\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are feeling strong, looking strong.\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had a record today - the shortest amount of time we have ever spent on the water for a race.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we are always improving.\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both men said that they had been thrilled to track Ireland's success thus far at the Olympics, with Mona McSharry (bronze) and Daniel Wiffen (gold) already taking home medals for Team Ireland.\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3437, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999907670916083, \"rank\": 3.78780575593243e-06, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 3486, \"end\": 3499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 3565, \"end\": 3577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.466268760703648e-13, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donovan has evensuggestedthat fellow rowers Daire Lynch and Philip Doyle are on for gold in the double sculls on Thursday morning.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3642, \"end\": 3654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Doyle_(American_football)\", \"score\": 0.809412548681283, \"rank\": 0.2243767313019458, \"text\": \"Philip Doyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil